Liverpool vs Arsenal has produced the most hat-tricks in Premier League history  . 
  Robbie Fowler scored the quickest hat-trick in the league against Arsenal in 1994 . 
  Thierry Henry scored a treble against Liverpool in 2004 at Highbury . 
  Andrey Arshavin scored a quadruple against the Reds in 2009 . 
  Martin Skrtel scored in Liverpool's 2-2 draw at Anfield in December . 
 